WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.314 --> 00:00:09.010
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:09.083 --> 00:00:12.951
<i>That's right. there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:13.020 --> 00:00:17.013
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:17.358 --> 00:00:19.849
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19.927 --> 00:00:23.988
<i>That's right. all the way to zero.</i>

6
00:00:24.065 --> 00:00:28.024
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:29.503 --> 00:00:34.236
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34.942 --> 00:00:37.911
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:40.348 --> 00:00:42.441
<i>It will reach you. without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:43.184 --> 00:00:44.481
<i>It will come. closer</i>

11
00:00:44.819 --> 00:00:47.379
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:55.429 --> 00:01:00.799
<i>We're speeding through life.</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:01.002 --> 00:01:02.162
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:02.236 --> 00:01:06.036
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:06.374 --> 00:01:11.573
<i>Even if I take it back. and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11.846 --> 00:01:13.177
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:13.247 --> 00:01:14.646
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14.715 --> 00:01:20.984
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:28.074
Support us and become VIP member 
to remove all ads from www.OpenSubtitles.org

20
00:01:33.856 --> 00:01:35.118
I like your determination!

21
00:01:36.358 --> 00:01:36.983
Then...

22
00:01:38.160 --> 00:01:39.957
For those who are still here...

23
00:01:41.196 --> 00:01:42.754
The first test...

24
00:01:45.934 --> 00:01:47.959
you have passed it!

25
00:01:55.444 --> 00:01:57.105
You've passed through the gates!

26
00:01:58.447 --> 00:02:01.814
The first test for the Chunin Exams
has been completed...

27
00:02:03.018 --> 00:02:06.010
I wish you well.

28
00:02:06.121 --> 00:02:08.783
All right! Wish us well!

29
00:02:13.428 --> 00:02:14.656
<i>What a funny guy...</i>

30
00:02:33.682 --> 00:02:34.478
<i>Huh...</i>

31
00:02:35.083 --> 00:02:37.074
<i>I didn't think that there would be</i>
<i>a guy who would pass the first test</i>

32
00:02:37.152 --> 00:02:38.244
<i>with a blank test sheet.</i>

33
00:02:39.087 --> 00:02:43.114
<i>Naruto Uzumaki.</i>
<i>He really is a funny guy.</i>

34
00:03:05.681 --> 00:03:11.517
<i>The Chunin Exam Stage 2.</i>
<i>The Forest of Death!</i>

35
00:03:20.429 --> 00:03:23.057
There's something kind
of creepy about this place.

36
00:03:25.067 --> 00:03:29.697
This place is called the Forest of Death.
you'll soon realize why.

37
00:03:32.474 --> 00:03:36.467
"The Forest of Death.
you'll soon realize why."

38
00:03:36.745 --> 00:03:39.737
That kind of threat won't work
on me one bit!

39
00:03:40.382 --> 00:03:42.009
I'm not scared!

40
00:03:43.251 --> 00:03:44.275
Really?

41
00:03:44.686 --> 00:03:46.813
You've got a lot of energy.

42
00:03:53.562 --> 00:03:57.464
A kid like you dies at very beginning.

43
00:03:59.801 --> 00:04:03.032
dappled with the red blood I like.

44
00:04:10.612 --> 00:04:13.103
I'm returning your... Kunai Knife...

45
00:04:13.882 --> 00:04:15.509
Thank you for taking the trouble...

46
00:04:23.859 --> 00:04:28.159
But... don't stand behind me.
thirsty for blood.

47
00:04:29.698 --> 00:04:31.893
If you don't want a quick death...

48
00:04:34.102 --> 00:04:38.664
Well. it's my nature to act up
at the sight of red blood.

49
00:04:39.741 --> 00:04:44.576
And my precious hair was cut.
so I got excited...

50
00:04:46.248 --> 00:04:47.180
Naruto...

51
00:04:48.150 --> 00:04:49.117
I'm sorry...

52
00:04:51.753 --> 00:04:53.983
<i>W-What with that Proctor?</i>

53
00:04:54.556 --> 00:04:55.853
<i>Frankly. she's psycho!</i>

54
00:04:56.725 --> 00:04:58.090
<i>This one. too...</i>

55
00:05:00.062 --> 00:05:02.257
<i>That girl. why was her tongue so long?</i>

56
00:05:04.032 --> 00:05:08.196
Evidently. we've got
a lot of hot blooded kids this time.

57
00:05:10.772 --> 00:05:12.137
This will be fun.

58
00:05:12.941 --> 00:05:15.967
You're the most hot blooded! Believe it!

59
00:05:18.313 --> 00:05:23.945
Well. before we start the second exam.
I have to pass this out to you!

60
00:05:30.392 --> 00:05:31.416
It's a consent form.

61
00:05:31.927 --> 00:05:35.795
before you can take part
in the test you have to sign this.

62
00:05:35.964 --> 00:05:36.760
Why?

63
00:05:37.399 --> 00:05:39.731
From here on out.
corpses are going to come out.

64
00:05:39.868 --> 00:05:42.359
I have to get your consent to that!

65
00:05:43.004 --> 00:05:45.370
Or it'll be my responsibility.

66
00:05:53.615 --> 00:05:56.550
Well. I'm going to start
the explanation for the second exam.

67
00:05:56.952 --> 00:06:01.321
In a word. the limits of
your survival will be challenged.

68
00:06:04.826 --> 00:06:09.195
<i>Survival. huh?</i>
<i>This test is a total pain.</i>

69
00:06:09.598 --> 00:06:13.796
First. I'll give you step-by-step instruction
on the terrain of this Training Field.

70
00:06:14.769 --> 00:06:19.468
Training Field Number 44 is surrounded
by 44 locked entrance gates.

71
00:06:19.541 --> 00:06:24.001
there are rivers and a forest
and a tower in the middle.

72
00:06:24.379 --> 00:06:27.473
It's about 10 kilometers
from the towers to the gate...

73
00:06:28.183 --> 00:06:32.779
In this confined area. you will
go through a certain survival program.

74
00:06:34.956 --> 00:06:36.651
The contents of which are...

75
00:06:40.829 --> 00:06:43.992
anything goes scroll battle!

76
00:06:45.033 --> 00:06:45.931
Scroll...?

77
00:06:46.001 --> 00:06:46.899
Yes...

78
00:06:48.136 --> 00:06:53.597
I want you to fight for two scrolls.
the Heaven Scroll and the Earth Scroll.

79
00:06:57.979 --> 00:07:01.676
All together 26 teams got
through the first test.

80
00:07:02.117 --> 00:07:03.584
Half of them...

81
00:07:03.652 --> 00:07:09.090
13 teams get the Heaven scroll.
the other half get the Earth Scroll.

82
00:07:09.291 --> 00:07:11.851
I'll hand over one scroll to each team.

83
00:07:12.527 --> 00:07:15.257
To put it simply.
that's what you're vying for.

84
00:07:16.064 --> 00:07:18.396
And the conditions to pass?

85
00:07:18.934 --> 00:07:23.598
Three of you bring both the Heaven and
Earth Scrolls to the tower in the center.

86
00:07:24.005 --> 00:07:29.910
That means that of the 13 teams.
half of them will fail for sure...

87
00:07:30.278 --> 00:07:32.246
Except it has to be in time.

88
00:07:32.881 --> 00:07:36.044
For this second exam.
the time limit is 120 hours.

89
00:07:36.484 --> 00:07:38.816
Do it in exactly five days!

90
00:07:38.920 --> 00:07:39.887
Five days.

91
00:07:39.955 --> 00:07:41.582
What do we do about food?

92
00:07:41.656 --> 00:07:44.955
Be self sufficient! It's a treasure trove
in the wilderness.

93
00:07:45.293 --> 00:07:46.954
There's more than enough for food...

94
00:07:47.462 --> 00:07:48.451
However...

95
00:07:49.164 --> 00:07:51.189
It's teeming with
fierce people eating animals.

96
00:07:51.466 --> 00:07:54.299
poison bugs. poisonous weeds and
much more.

97
00:07:54.636 --> 00:07:56.069
No way...

98
00:07:56.171 --> 00:07:59.368
Fool. that's why it's called survival!

99
00:07:59.841 --> 00:08:05.177
Besides. it's improbable that 39 people.
13 teams will pass.

100
00:08:05.780 --> 00:08:08.544
The interval for activity gets longer
with passing each day.

101
00:08:08.783 --> 00:08:12.184
while the time for recovery
gets shorter...

102
00:08:12.554 --> 00:08:14.249
Seems pretty grueling!

103
00:08:16.291 --> 00:08:18.623
On top of that. you're surrounded
by nothing but enemies.

104
00:08:18.727 --> 00:08:21.321
even falling asleep
will be a problem...

105
00:08:21.696 --> 00:08:25.757
And. besides those injured
during attempts to capture scrolls...

106
00:08:26.167 --> 00:08:27.930
there will definitely be people

107
00:08:28.003 --> 00:08:30.938
are unable to endure
the rigors of the course.

108
00:08:31.573 --> 00:08:35.031
Umm... so you can quit in the middle of it?

109
00:08:35.677 --> 00:08:39.044
According to the rules.
you cannot give up in the middle of it!

110
00:08:39.514 --> 00:08:42.677
I want you to spend
five days in the forest.

111
00:08:43.184 --> 00:08:45.015
Just like I thought...

112
00:08:45.620 --> 00:08:47.713
This is going to be a pain!

113
00:08:48.223 --> 00:08:51.158
Moving on. conditions of disqualification.

114
00:08:51.726 --> 00:08:55.594
Number 1. if all three members
of the team can't make it to the tower

115
00:08:55.664 --> 00:08:58.758
with the Heaven and Earth Scrolls
within the time limit.

116
00:08:59.734 --> 00:09:05.934
Number 2. if a team loses a member
or if a member became incapacitated.

117
00:09:06.708 --> 00:09:08.733
There's that. and this is a supplement...

118
00:09:09.110 --> 00:09:11.578
Absolutely do not look at
the contents of the scrolls

119
00:09:11.646 --> 00:09:13.671
until you have reached the tower!

120
00:09:14.582 --> 00:09:17.608
W-What happens if we look
at it halfway through?

121
00:09:18.219 --> 00:09:22.986
When you look at it you'll find... out!

122
00:09:23.491 --> 00:09:24.389
Huh?

123
00:09:25.894 --> 00:09:30.024
There are times when a Chunin
must deal with super secret text.

124
00:09:30.298 --> 00:09:32.198
This is to test your reliability.

125
00:09:32.701 --> 00:09:33.725
That's all the explanation!

126
00:09:34.002 --> 00:09:37.233
I'll exchange your three consent forms for
the scrolls in that hut over there.

127
00:09:37.972 --> 00:09:42.068
After that. pick your entrance.
and all the gates will open simultaneously!

128
00:09:45.714 --> 00:09:48.148
Finally. just a word of advice...

129
00:09:49.417 --> 00:09:50.179
Don't die!

130
00:10:15.944 --> 00:10:20.404
<i>I see. so you won't know which</i>
<i>scroll was given to each team...</i>

131
00:10:20.648 --> 00:10:25.381
<i>and you won't know which of</i>
<i>the three people is carrying the scroll.</i>

132
00:10:26.421 --> 00:10:28.150
<i>If what lbiki said was right.</i>

133
00:10:28.390 --> 00:10:32.520
<i>there will be life or death</i>
<i>struggles for information in this test.</i>

134
00:10:34.729 --> 00:10:35.855
<i>Everyone is an enemy!</i>

135
00:10:40.101 --> 00:10:41.932
<i>The resolve of everyone here is strong.</i>

136
00:10:43.138 --> 00:10:45.197
<i>That means that it might come</i>
<i>to killing each other.</i>

137
00:10:48.443 --> 00:10:51.378
<i>It looks like they understand the meaning</i>
<i>of the consent form a little bit...</i>

138
00:10:56.251 --> 00:10:58.549
Heeey. look who's here!

139
00:10:58.753 --> 00:11:01.085
It's Billboard Brow. isn't it?

140
00:11:01.890 --> 00:11:07.089
I thought you went home long ago.
I never imagined you were still here.

141
00:11:07.695 --> 00:11:11.825
Ooooh? Look who's here.
the ugly Inopig

142
00:11:12.167 --> 00:11:15.796
Starting now. it's five days of
the survival test with Sasuke.

143
00:11:16.037 --> 00:11:18.301
There's no reason to go home.

144
00:11:21.976 --> 00:11:22.806
- Ugly!
- Billboard!

145
00:11:22.877 --> 00:11:23.844
- Ugly! Ugly!
- Billboard! Billboard!

146
00:11:23.912 --> 00:11:25.436
- Ugly. ugly. ugly!
- Billboard. billboard. billboard!

147
00:11:25.513 --> 00:11:27.208
- Billboard. billboard. billboard!
- Ugly ugly ugly!

148
00:11:27.282 --> 00:11:29.273
- Ugly. ugly. ugly. ugly!
- Billboard. billboard. billboard. billboard!

149
00:11:29.651 --> 00:11:31.414
Sakura. this is impossible for you.

150
00:11:31.486 --> 00:11:33.954
For your own sake.
just hurry up and go home!

151
00:11:34.355 --> 00:11:36.414
I could say the exact same thing to you!

152
00:11:43.431 --> 00:11:46.764
Hey. why are those two
on such bad terms?

153
00:11:47.268 --> 00:11:50.465
D-Do you think I care about
something stupid like that?

154
00:11:52.841 --> 00:11:56.106
Man... all there is to do
is write my name.

155
00:11:56.177 --> 00:11:58.168
why does it take this much time!

156
00:12:00.114 --> 00:12:03.174
Hey! Hinata! What are you
doing over there?

157
00:12:04.886 --> 00:12:06.148
N-Naruto...

158
00:12:07.021 --> 00:12:09.387
Umm... uhhhh... well...

159
00:12:09.924 --> 00:12:12.654
<i>Just like I thought.</i>
<i>this kid is strange.</i>

160
00:12:14.729 --> 00:12:15.423
A scratch...

161
00:12:15.730 --> 00:12:18.995
Uh um... this... is

162
00:12:19.067 --> 00:12:20.034
See ya!

163
00:12:25.507 --> 00:12:26.633
Naruto...

164
00:12:29.177 --> 00:12:31.873
It's about time for
the scroll exchange.

165
00:12:44.225 --> 00:12:47.058
<i>Well. I wonder how</i>
<i>many teams will survive...</i>

166
00:13:00.041 --> 00:13:01.838
Teams who have
taken the scroll.

167
00:13:01.910 --> 00:13:04.902
stay with the representative
and move to the gate!

168
00:13:05.079 --> 00:13:07.980
We'll all start simultaneously
in 30 minutes!!

169
00:13:18.914 --> 00:13:22.509
Yeah! Survival is our forte!

170
00:13:22.685 --> 00:13:25.085
Hinata. don't show your weakness.

171
00:13:26.288 --> 00:13:27.084
Uh. okay...

172
00:13:28.157 --> 00:13:29.419
Life or death...

173
00:13:29.792 --> 00:13:32.192
It's a pain but we just have to do this.

174
00:13:32.795 --> 00:13:34.820
Since it's come to this.
Naruto will be our target.

175
00:13:35.197 --> 00:13:38.132
For snacks. there's potato chips...

176
00:13:38.300 --> 00:13:39.824
- What about shortcake.?
- <i>I can't believe you two!</i>

177
00:13:41.270 --> 00:13:43.864
Okaaaay! I won't lose!

178
00:13:44.306 --> 00:13:47.742
I'll bring down whoever comes near me.

179
00:13:47.876 --> 00:13:51.107
- Yes!
- Cha!

180
00:13:55.384 --> 00:13:58.012
Heh heh... finally the opportunity is here...

181
00:13:58.520 --> 00:14:01.785
We have the chance to fulfill
our mission in earnest...

182
00:14:08.464 --> 00:14:09.988
<i>Sure. the enemy teams are scary but.</i>

183
00:14:10.766 --> 00:14:13.599
<i>I'm really scared of spending</i>
<i>five days with this guy.</i>

184
00:14:16.305 --> 00:14:18.500
Target the rookies first.

185
00:14:19.341 --> 00:14:21.434
They said that from now on
it's okay to kill.

186
00:14:21.510 --> 00:14:22.943
which makes it easier.

187
00:14:26.115 --> 00:14:31.314
<i>Master Guy. I'll do my best!</i>
<i>I'll definitely succeed!</i>

188
00:14:44.733 --> 00:14:49.466
We now start the second
test of the Chunin Exam!

189
00:14:53.909 --> 00:14:55.069
Look for the brats!

190
00:14:55.377 --> 00:14:56.844
Those three. right?

191
00:14:59.114 --> 00:15:01.378
All right! Let's go!

192
00:15:11.360 --> 00:15:14.056
Okay! First. we search for that thing.

193
00:15:14.396 --> 00:15:15.761
Can you do it. Hinata?

194
00:15:16.131 --> 00:15:16.756
Yes.

195
00:15:20.302 --> 00:15:21.166
Byakugan!

196
00:15:24.473 --> 00:15:27.670
Slow down. Lee!
We just started.

197
00:15:28.143 --> 00:15:30.270
I know. But...

198
00:15:31.713 --> 00:15:33.146
I can't stay still!

199
00:15:33.582 --> 00:15:36.073
Who knows what kind of
powerful foe is waiting for us.

200
00:15:38.053 --> 00:15:39.384
Hot-blooded fool...

201
00:15:40.522 --> 00:15:43.218
As you already understand.
we have only one target!

202
00:15:58.440 --> 00:16:00.806
W-What are you doing. Choji?

203
00:16:03.178 --> 00:16:07.205
Just a little break...
I'm already tired. and hungry...

204
00:16:07.616 --> 00:16:10.312
What are you suddenly saying?!

205
00:16:10.686 --> 00:16:13.246
It hasn't been five minutes
since we started!

206
00:16:13.989 --> 00:16:17.117
But I can't help it. I'm hungry...

207
00:16:17.659 --> 00:16:21.095
You! If you were able to bring snacks.

208
00:16:21.163 --> 00:16:24.929
you should have been able
to bring one Kunai knife!

209
00:16:25.234 --> 00:16:26.064
Ino! Hide!

210
00:16:42.050 --> 00:16:42.914
<i>Uh oh!</i>

211
00:16:53.395 --> 00:16:55.761
<i>This kind of thing continuing</i>
<i>for five days...?</i>

212
00:17:05.207 --> 00:17:08.973
Anyway. the tower is the
goal for everyone. right?

213
00:17:09.711 --> 00:17:13.272
So it would be clever for us to make
a trap in the vicinity of the tower.

214
00:17:14.883 --> 00:17:17.716
Okay... wasting no time. huh?

215
00:17:18.487 --> 00:17:19.317
Where are they?

216
00:17:21.490 --> 00:17:23.185
Heh... kids.

217
00:17:23.725 --> 00:17:26.819
It's like begging to be found.
standing in that conspicuous place.

218
00:17:27.062 --> 00:17:29.292
They sensed our presence.

219
00:17:29.865 --> 00:17:33.198
but. evidently they haven't
grasped where we are.

220
00:17:34.603 --> 00:17:36.662
What happened?
You're pale.

221
00:17:40.309 --> 00:17:41.708
W-What is that?!

222
00:17:52.187 --> 00:17:55.679
The Flying Leeches of Leaf Village
sense body temperature and perspiration.

223
00:17:55.757 --> 00:17:57.657
then in mass. swoop down
on their prey.

224
00:17:58.427 --> 00:18:00.691
If they continue to suck
your blood for five minutes.

225
00:18:00.762 --> 00:18:01.956
you go to the other world...

226
00:18:02.831 --> 00:18:04.594
Using this behavior.

227
00:18:04.666 --> 00:18:07.226
we'd set a trap on the path
enemies would use to escape.

228
00:18:07.836 --> 00:18:10.236
D-Damn it...

229
00:18:16.478 --> 00:18:17.775
That's one team gone!

230
00:18:27.456 --> 00:18:29.287
It sounds like they've already started.

231
00:18:32.794 --> 00:18:35.024
Wasn't that someone screaming
just now?

232
00:18:40.769 --> 00:18:43.397
I-I'm kinda getting nervous.

233
00:18:44.006 --> 00:18:48.272
I-It was nothing. Sakura.
Believe it!

234
00:18:50.645 --> 00:18:52.909
I-I have to pee...

235
00:18:53.615 --> 00:18:55.139
Y-You... fool!

236
00:18:55.550 --> 00:18:58.110
What are you doing
in front of a lady!

237
00:18:58.353 --> 00:18:59.718
Go to the grass!

238
00:19:06.395 --> 00:19:09.990
Aaah. that was a lot!
I'm refreshed.

239
00:19:10.132 --> 00:19:13.067
Like I said. not in front of a lady!

240
00:19:19.041 --> 00:19:22.533
S-Sasuke... no matter what.
you don't have to go that far.

241
00:19:23.879 --> 00:19:25.073
W-What was that for...?

242
00:19:36.124 --> 00:19:38.524
What are you doing... all of a sudden?!

243
00:19:38.794 --> 00:19:41.695
What you ask? That's my line. isn't it?

244
00:19:42.130 --> 00:19:42.858
Sasuke!

245
00:19:43.732 --> 00:19:45.359
It can't be helped!

246
00:19:57.813 --> 00:19:59.781
Sasuke. please stop!

247
00:20:00.415 --> 00:20:01.677
Look closely at him!

248
00:20:04.920 --> 00:20:07.286
Talk! Where's the real Naruto!

249
00:20:08.657 --> 00:20:11.285
I have no idea what
you're talking about!

250
00:20:11.460 --> 00:20:12.927
What happened to the scratch
on you face?

251
00:20:16.131 --> 00:20:20.124
I'm asking what happened to the scratch
you got before from the Proctor!

252
00:20:20.669 --> 00:20:24.264
And your Shuriken holster
is on your left leg.

253
00:20:24.773 --> 00:20:26.240
That guy's right handed!

254
00:20:28.543 --> 00:20:32.570
You're worse at transformation
than Naruto. you phony!

255
00:20:35.217 --> 00:20:38.948
Unlucky! You got me.
In that case...

256
00:20:39.654 --> 00:20:41.679
Which one of you got the scroll?

257
00:20:44.326 --> 00:20:48.057
If you listen to me obediently.
I'll spare your lives.

258
00:20:53.902 --> 00:20:57.668
I see! Then I'll resort to force!

259
00:21:06.111 --> 00:21:10.707
<i>Hey. can you hear it?</i>

260
00:21:10.816 --> 00:21:18.916
<i>The clear. blue sky goes on and on</i>

261
00:21:19.991 --> 00:21:28.524
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

262
00:21:29.134 --> 00:21:36.836
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

263
00:21:38.243 --> 00:21:43.772
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

264
00:21:43.849 --> 00:21:47.615
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

265
00:21:47.686 --> 00:21:51.247
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

266
00:21:51.723 --> 00:22:00.131
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

267
00:22:00.532 --> 00:22:05.595
<i>when you want to cry. and you want to run away</i>

268
00:22:05.670 --> 00:22:10.073
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

269
00:22:10.242 --> 00:22:13.905
<i>Just sing.</i>

270
00:22:14.212 --> 00:22:19.309
<i>Light is born. and darkness was born</i>

271
00:22:19.451 --> 00:22:21.578
<i>The two are one</i>

272
00:22:21.686 --> 00:22:27.955
<i>Harmonia. feel the telepathy</i>

273
00:22:28.560 --> 00:22:33.554
<i>Hey. can you hear it?</i>

274
00:22:38.387 --> 00:22:40.582
Aww. stupid gas mask man!

275
00:22:41.090 --> 00:22:43.718
Suddenly sneaking up on someone
when they're peeing!

276
00:22:43.826 --> 00:22:45.760
I messed up just a little bit.

277
00:22:45.894 --> 00:22:48.124
Now I have to hurry and
meet up with Sakura.

278
00:22:48.230 --> 00:22:50.664
Wait a minute!
What is this giant snake?

279
00:22:50.766 --> 00:22:53.360
Hey! Are you serious?!
Wait a minute. hey!

280
00:22:54.770 --> 00:22:56.203
I've been gulped down!

281
00:22:57.506 --> 00:23:00.805
Next episode: "Eat or Be Eaten:
Panic in the Forest"

282
00:23:01.110 --> 00:23:03.874
Will I return to action?!

283
00:23:04.305 --> 00:24:04.704
